@node CHANGES "History"

    @{FG shine}- History -@{FG text}


  @{b}ver. 2.6@{ub}  - added the support for DOpus Magellan II (the batch file can
              be shared between AmFTP and DOpus). However I think to have
              done a little mess with the AmFTP support :(

            - removed other small bugs


  @{b}ver. 2.5@{ub}  - added the possibility to set the Reply to: field in
              ftp-emails

            - fixed the "dimagrone" bug :) (the one that sometime makes the
              window narrow and then it cannot be resized anymore)

            - I think (=hope :) ) to have fixed the tiny arrows problem that
              sometime produces a crash of the program (on my system
              the program doesn't crash anymore)

            - resolved the problem with ftp-emails creation (on some
              sistems there were very serious crashes or create empty
              emails)

            - removed other small bugs

            - now the program is a bit faster when it fills the two lists


  @{b}ver. 2.42@{ub} - changed a bit the settings window to let it open
              also on low resolution screens

            - added Deutsch install script

            - fixed a bubble help text


  @{b}ver. 2.41@{ub} - fixed a bug when creating ftp-mails


  @{b}ver. 2.4@{ub}  - added Spanish guide (10x to Triskelion)

            - added automatic download with AmFTP

            - fixed some bugs

            - no more problems with rx command (now is no more needed)


  @{b}ver 2.3@{ub}   - now you can multiselect recents and load all the archives in one time
              (10x to Marcel Beck for the new ARexx command :)

            - added French amigaguide (10x to Chapron Jean-Michel)

            - added the support for "wget -c -i file.list" invocation style of wget

            - added Hungarian catalog (10x to Kovŕc Péter)

            - you can decide the sender of recent emails (so if Aminet main server
              changes in the future, you can adapt the program to it)

            - added Spanish catalog (10x to Triskelion)

  @{b}ver 2.2@{ub}   - fixed a stupid bug in settings window

            - added two buttons to load next/previous recent and a button
              to load the selected recent in Yam folder

            - added French catalog (10x to Chapron Jean-Michel)

            - support for XPK-Packed folders

            - new options in Ftp-emails generator

            - fixed some nasty bugs


