              and Veronica Oksholen)

            - fixed Deutsch catalog (10x to Micharl Lunse)

            - GUI has changed, now uses NList.mcc (10x to Gilles Masson)

            - added extra MWB-Icons (10x to Marco Scharfchen)

            - send html files to browser with OpenURL.library (10x to
