            - changed documentation


  @{b}ver. 1.9@{ub}  - added an Italian version with doc

            - nuked the bug of the Html file generator

            - it doesn't do rubbish in @{b}t:@{ub}

            - in the Ftp-Section now is possible to view the AmFtp
              batch file and delete it

