  @{b}ver. 1.6@{ub}  - fixed a lot of bugs :)

            - now works fine with MUIRexx @{FG text}3.0a@{FG text} (or it seems to work fine :))


  @{b}ver. 1.4@{ub}  - fixed the install script bug that doesn't copy the
